content/chapter-04/NestedAggregationQuer.body:
Nested Aggregations

Example of nested aggregation query, terms and histogram:curl -XPOST 'localhost:9200/ordering/order/_search?pretty=true' -d '
{
"size": 0,
"aggs": {
  "order-status": {
    "terms": {
    "field": "status"
    },
    "aggs": {
      "placedOnMonth": {
          "date_histogram" : {
            "field": "placedOn",
            "interval": "month",
            "format": "YYYY-MM"
           }
      }
    }
  }
}
}
'

